eam\", \"score\": 0.7709345343229115, \"rank\": 0.29709867036115717, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif is one of two athletes - along with Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting - who have been cleared to compete having been disqualified from last year's Women's World Championships after they were said to have failed gender eligibility tests.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9738826391688473, \"rank\": 0.02673451079707563, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hungarian Boxing Association has protested against Khelif's participation at Paris 2024, and the Hungarian Olympic Committee requested talks with the International Olympic Committee (IOC) over the issue.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999999550478252, \"rank\": 4.439747918029922e-07, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.9999999996257429, \"rank\": 3.740384845333615e-10, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.348499938297976e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hungarian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kheireddine Barbari, the head of the Algerian delegation at the Paris Olympics, said the Algerian Olympic Committee had filed a complaint with the IOC over the \\\"immoral\\\" campaign against Khelif.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7709345343229115, \"rank\": 0.29709867036115717, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Algerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.20372272839623e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamori wrote on social media: \\\"In my humble opinion, I do not think it's fair that this contestant can compete in the women's category.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I cannot concern myself with that now.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot change it, it's life.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can promise you one thing...\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will do my best to win and I will fight as long as I can!\\\"\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamori has beaten Ireland's Grainne Walsh and Australian Marissa Williamson to reach the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9852757618163099, \"rank\": 0.01006012604810111, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9802289353963053, \"rank\": 0.020164850879748265, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\", \"score\": 0.9999999899982868, \"rank\": 1.0001716796461353e-08, \"text\": \"Marissa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marissa_Cooper\"}, {\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1291047793316177e-13, \"text\": \"Williamson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zion_Williamson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has previously fought at the 2018 Youth Olympic Games and was a silver medallist in the 66kg class at the 2022 European Under-22 Championships.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1490, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9631096363299525, \"rank\": 0.03830338964402225, \"text\": \"2022 European\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_European_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin's next opponent also criticised the fact that she has to face a boxer whose participation at the Olympics has been questioned.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the quarter-finals, Lin faces Svetlana Kamenova Staneva of Bulgaria on Sunday morning.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.942560489826769, \"rank\": 0.06093986619382174, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the situation in this category, which, you know, people are talking about all over Facebook, the internet and media, this is not good for women's boxing,\\\" Staneva said.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Bulgarian Boxing Federation spokesperson added: \\\"We believe that athletes should be placed on an equal level in any competition, especially when it comes to the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9999997695245194, \"rank\": 2.295680907695215e-07, \"text\": \"Bulgarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the case of Imane Khalif and Lin Yu-ting, we see no such equal treatment and strongly oppose their participation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing controversy - what we know and what we do not  I want to apologise to Khelif - Italian boxer Carini  Lin wins controversial first bout at Paris Olympics  Both Lin and Khelif made it through to the Olympic quarter-finals in comfortable fashion.\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9366670498670431, \"rank\": 0.04467406961116176, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9550154954612589, \"rank\": 0.04710342895234599, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif beat Angela Carini in the first round of competition as the Italian abandoned their bout after 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9366670498670431, \"rank\": 0.04467406961116176, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini said on Thursday she ended the fight to \\\"preserve her life\\\", butapologised to her opponent on Friday, saying \\\"if the IOC said she can fight, I respect that decision\\\".\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9550154954612589, \"rank\": 0.04710342895234599, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2718, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.20372272839623e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin, 28,dominated Uzbekistan's Sitora Turdibekovain the 57kg category on Friday.\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.9999901917543755, \"rank\": 9.803678900796946e-06, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russia-led International Boxing Association (IBA), which carried out the eligibility tests last year, said Khelif and Lin \\\"failed to meet the eligibility criteria for participating in the women's competition, as set and laid out in the IBA regulations\\\".\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0504378777404068e-30, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2900, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999706593405607, \"rank\": 2.9337150703880355e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 3091, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999706593405607, \"rank\": 2.9337150703880355e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin and Khelif were banned, the IBA has said, \\\"to uphold the level of fairness and utmost integrity of the competition\\\".\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3142, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999706593405607, \"rank\": 2.9337150703880355e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin was stripped of a bronze medal at last year's World Championships.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last June,the IBA was stripped of its statusas the sport's world governing body by the IOC.\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999706593405607, \"rank\": 2.9337150703880355e-05, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 3390, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.20372272839623e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC, which defines gender by how it is recorded on an athlete's passport, said the pair were \\\"suddenly disqualified without any due process\\\".\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3400, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Internationa